Microsoft=E2=80=99s gain, meanwhile, is OpenAI=E2=80=99s loss, which is dep=
endent on the Redmond-based company for both money and compute: the work it=
s employees will do on AI will either be Microsoft=E2=80=99s by virtue of t=
hat perpetual license, or Microsoft=E2=80=99s directly because said employe=
